<view class="container">
  <view class="card">
    <view class="eyebrow">Medical Content Studio</view>
    <view class="h1">医学科普文章工作台</view>
    <view class="muted" style="margin-top: 20rpx;">登录后可保存草稿、整理科普结构，并生成 AI 写作提示词。</view>

    <view class="label">用户名</view>
    <input class="input" value="{{username}}" bindinput="onUsername" placeholder="例如 yuqian" />

    <view class="label">密码</view>
    <input class="input" value="{{password}}" bindinput="onPassword" password placeholder="至少 6 位" />

    <view class="btn-row">
      <button class="btn" bindtap="login">登录</button>
      <button class="btn secondary" bindtap="register">注册</button>
    </view>

    <view class="muted" style="margin-top: 24rpx; font-size: 24rpx;">本地调试使用 127.0.0.1:3000；上线前请在 app.js 里换成 HTTPS 云端地址。</view>
  </view>
</view>
